  <name>London Congestion Charging Zone</name>
  <description><![CDATA[I made this map for my own convenience. Feel free to use it, if you think it will be useful: but be aware that it isn't accurate to any greater resolution than I need for my purposes, and I probably won't bother updating it until I personally need to. So don't rely on it for anything crucial, but do feel free to copy it and edit your own copy.]]></description>
